{
  "stem": "7093.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so a, a few days later, on the 29th of April, I managed to get enough on my feet that, with his help and a stick, I could walk a little bit.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we started to walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then a tractor came with two open lorries.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on these two open lorries, something miraculous happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because there was a French flag.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were 38 French people-- 10 French women who came from concentration camp and 28 men who were prisoners of war-- who were on this lorry pulled by the tractor.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And because my companion was French, they took us up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were now a group of 40 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a group of 40 people with transport, we arrived in Wurzen, which was the, the-- it was-- should I spell it perhaps?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "W-U-R-Z-E-N, which was a town where there was a liberation-- American liberation center.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were officially liberated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know all dates taken-- everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said because we are a group of 40, and because we have our own transport, they won't retain us at Wurzen or won't send us in DP camps.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we can move on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave us vouchers to requisition food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they gave us vouchers to requisition lodging.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we moved on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a few days later, we arrived in Metz, which was the official French reception center for people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were the first 11 women, 11 French women-- I wasn't French, but 11 women-- who came from a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now because I wasn't French and because I wasn't going to go to Paris, but I, I was with this man, who was from Toulon, I-- they, they didn't send me away.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the other 10 women, they sent them by airplane to Paris.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
